General Richard O'Donovan, The O'Donovan1

M, #341704, b. 1768, d. November 1829

Last Edited=12 Mar 2009

Consanguinity Index=0.39%

General Richard O'Donovan, The O'Donovan was born in 1768.1 He was the son of Daniel O'Donovan, The O'Donovan and Jane Becher.1 He married Emma Ann Powell, daughter of Robert Powell.1 He died in November 1829, without issue.1

He held the position of Chief of the Clan Cathal from in 1778.1 He gained the rank of General in the 6th Dragoons.1 He fought in the Napoleonic Wars, in campaigns in Flanders and Spain.1
